    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior paint still holds a nice shine, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches near the door handles from regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors, with only minor wear on the driver's seat bolster and some light scuffing on the plastic trim. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a solid service history, making it a dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle.",
