    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of unparalleled distinction, preserved in absolute showroom condition. This motorcar represents the pinnacle of its class, exhibiting no discernible wear and maintaining the precise mechanical integrity of a factory-fresh unit. Meticulously curated and stored in a climate-controlled environment, it offers the discerning buyer a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of investment-grade quality. We invite you to experience the uncompromising excellence of this masterfully maintained automobile.",
      "price": 46500.0,
