    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. It is honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere! I've babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. I'm really sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be so happy with it. Feel free to message me if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
