    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-grade vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, protected by a premium ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time capsule' condition; the leather seats retain their original matte finish and factory scent, with no creases or signs of wear. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. Mechanically, the car is flawless, accompanied by a comprehensive binder of service records from authorized technicians. This isn't just a used car; it is a museum-quality specimen for the discerning collector who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
